µC1Method: Scripts and viewersµC4

This is a modification of portable demos. If you want to make lots of demos that use the same set of routines, you might make each demo a package with script, graphics and music, which is opened with a viewer. You only have to make the viewer once on each platform and it may use any amount of assembly and machine-specific optimization. However, it is hard work getting it right since you almost have to invent a new programming language.

