µC1Method: Distribution of moviesµC4

Demos are already largely distributed as captured divx movies, making them viewable on most machines. However the movies are very bulky files, 50MB for any demo, so only broadband owners will want to download them and only few will want them lying around on the harddisk. But of course you can burn a dozen of them on a cheap CDR. But then again, are you motivated to that? I propose that someone starts a mailorder distribution that sells CDRs with demo-divx collections, like in the good old PD-disk days!

